  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink45-kilavi">neṭunāḷ parattaiyariṭattaṉāy oḻukiya talaimakaṉ maṉaivayiṟ ceṉṟuḻit tōḻi
          colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink45">
          <l>kūti rāyiṟ ṟaṇkaliḻ tantu</l>
          <l>vēṉi lāyiṉ maṇiniṟaṅ koḷḷum</l>
          <l>yāṟaṇin taṉṟuniṉ ṉūrē</l>
          <l>pacappaṇin taṉavāṉ makiḻnaveṉ kaṇṇē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">

<l>           Your village is adorned with a river</l> 
<l>           that produces cool, muddy water in winter</l> 
<l>           [and] adopts the [clear blue] colour of sapphire in summer.</l> 
<l>           [But] my eyes, o delightful man, are adorned only with pallor. </l> 
          


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
